nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 139 is the 117th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 47th published by Titan Magazines. It was released on January 29, 2013.

Season Five of Star Wars: The Clone Wars intensifies as Obi-Wan Kenobi joins forces with the Mandalorians. We preview the all-new episodes. We're also taking a look behind the scenes on the Making of Return of the Jedi, with exclusive content from J. W. Rinzler's forthcoming book. Exclusive classic behind-the-scenes material, and exclusive fiction continues with all-new art!
